             Please note it may take up to 48 hours for tracking to display on the UPS’s website. There may be several days when it appears your package is not moving to its destination. This occurs when your package is on a long haul truck or on a train. The tracking of your package is only updated when it reaches the next distribution center. It can take several days for a truck or train to arrive in Canada from San Jose, California.
          </p>
          <p class="font-bold">
             <em>How did my package ship?</em>
          </p>
          <p>
             All orders are shipped with UPS WorldWide Expedited. The UPS tracking number will be emailed to you.
          </p>
          <p class="font-bold">
             <em>How do I track my packaged?</em>
          </p>
          <p>
             Click <a class="thin-u-l" href="https://www.ups.com/tracking/tracking.html">HERE</a> to track your package. Your ship confirmation email includes your UPS tracking number. Your confirmation email also has a link to track your package.
          </p>
          <p class="font-bold">
             <em>What do I do if my package does not arrive in the estimated timeframe?</em>
          </p>
          <p>
             All UPS WorldWide Expedited packages should land on your doorstep within 4 - 7 <strong>business</strong> days. The estimated time of delivery can be delayed due to weather. road conditions or customs inspecting your package.. The carrier’s web site will often state if packages are being delayed due to weather.
          </p>
          <p>
             If tracking of your package has been updating and then shows no movement, it is possible your package: 1) is pending a customs inspection, 2) has an incorrect address or is missing address information, and 3) it has been damaged or lost by the carrier.
          </p>
          <p>
             If the tracking number shows your package has been delivered and you have not received it, please check around your yard and home, and with your neighbors. UPS may leave a package in places where they think it will be safe, for example behind a side gate, under a bush, etc.
          </p>
          <p>
             If you cannot locate your package, please contact us at <a class="thin-u-l" href="mailto:customerservice@puritycosmetics.com">customerservice@puritycosmetics.com</a> or <a class="thin-u-l" href="tel:+14158149788">415-814-9788</a>.
